result.execSummary:
The defendant Chantil M. Rahlf was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Chantil M. Rahlf is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Chantil M. Rahlf was found guilty of Possess/Illegally Obtained Prescription, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 450.11(7)(h).
  • Chantil M. Rahlf was found guilty of Resisting or Obstructing an Officer, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.41(1).
